7
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:30,471
Joyce Godenzi, Ha Chi-chun, Charlie
Chin Hsiang-lin, Billy Lau Nam-kwang,

8
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,710
Corey Yuen Kwai, Lam Ching-ying,
